description: (Enterprise Tier Only) Commands to manage job executions of Azure Spring Apps service.

commands.name: az spring job execution cancel
examples: az spring job execution cancel -n job-execution-name --job job-name -s MyAzureSpringAppsInstance -g MyResourceGroup

commands.name: az spring job execution list
commands.summary: List all executions of the job.
examples: az spring job execution list --job job-name -s MyAzureSpringAppsInstance -g MyResourceGroup

commands.name: az spring job execution show
commands.summary: Show status and results of an execution of the job.
examples: az spring job execution show -n job-execution-name --job job-name -s MyAzureSpringAppsInstance -g MyResourceGroup
